    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is mechanically pristine, mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with treated shells, and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, supported by fresh OEM bushings and dampers. The exterior finish is flawless, showing deep luster across all panels with no signs of oxidation or wear. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster fatigue. A turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
