      "description": "This is a true collector-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Finished in its original, high-gloss paint with absolutely no stone chips or blemishes, the exterior is laser-straight and retains a deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is detailed to a concours standard. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, comes with a complete folder of exhaustive service records from day one, and has never been driven in inclement weather. It is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle that requires zero investment\u2014just a turn of the key.",
